text: Laurence Hourdel (born 18 August 1965) is a French rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
